questions.text:
Quyidagi kodning konsolga chiqishi qanday bo‘ladi? ```js
const arr = [1, 2, 3];
const x = arr.push(4);
console.log(x, arr);
```

slice() va splice() farqini to‘g‘ri ifodalagan natijani toping. Kod natijasi nima? ```js
const a = [10, 20, 30, 40, 50];
const b = a.slice(1, 4);
const c = a.splice(2, 2, 99);
console.log(b, a, c);
```

shift() va unshift() bilan ishlaganda natija qanday? ```js
const q = ['a','b','c'];
const r = q.shift();
const s = q.unshift('z');
console.log(r, s, q);
```

pop() funksiyasi qaytaradigan qiymatni aniqlang. ```js
let nums = [5, 6, 7];
const out = nums.pop();
console.log(out, nums.length, nums);
```

split() va join() zanjiri natijasini toping. ```js
const s = "a,b,c,,d";
const arr = s.split(",");
const t = arr.filter(x => x !== "").join("-");
console.log(arr.length, t);
```

splice bilan o‘rtaga bir nechta element qo‘shish natijasini toping. ```js
const a = [1,2,5,6];
console.log(a);
```

slice() manfiy indekslar bilan qanday ishlaydi? Natijani toping. ```js
const a = [10,20,30,40,50];
console.log(a.slice(-3, -1));
```

push() va unshift() birga qo‘llanganda massiv tartibi qanday bo‘ladi? ```js
const a = [2];
console.log(a);
```

Object bilan ishlash: property o‘chirilgandan keyingi natija. ```js
const user = {name:'Ali', age:20, city:'Toshkent'};
delete user.age;
console.log('age' in user, Object.keys(user).length);
```

Massivdan faqat yagona qiymatlarni qoldirish. Quyidagi kodning chiqishi? ```js
const arr = ['a','b','a','c','b','a'];
const uniq = [...new Set(arr)];
console.log(uniq);
```

splice bilan oxirgi ikkita elementni olib tashlash. ```js
const a = [1,2,3,4,5];
const removed = a.splice(-2);
console.log(removed, a);
```

slice va length bilan nusxa olish. Natija? ```js
const a = [1,2,3];
const b = a.slice();
console.log(a, b);
```

Object destructuring: to‘g‘ri natijani toping. ```js
const obj = {a:1, b:2};
const {a:x=0, c:y=5} = obj;
console.log(x, y);
```

Array.from bilan stringni massivga aylantirish: chiqish? ```js
const s = '00510';
const arr = Array.from(s, ch => Number(ch));
console.log(arr.filter(n => n).length);
```

splice bilan almashtirish: ```js
const a = ['x','y','z','t'];
console.log(a);
```

split limit bilan: ```js
const s = "1-2-3-4";
console.log(s.split('-', 2));
```

unshift va shift ketma-ketligi natijasi: ```js
const a = [];
console.log(a);
```

Object.assign bilan yuzaki nusxa va birlashtirish: ```js
const a = {x:1, y:{z:2}};
const b = Object.assign({}, a);
console.log(a.y.z, b.y.z);
```

Array.prototype.splice qaytarayotgan qiymat. ```js
const a = [1,2,3,4];
const r = a.splice(1, 2);
console.log(r);
```

push() return qiymati va massiv holati: ```js
let a = [0];
const len = a.push(1,2);
console.log(len, a[1]);
```

Object kalitlarini tartibda olish: ```js
const o = {b:2, a:1, c:3};
console.log(Object.keys(o));
```

split() bo‘sh joylar bilan: ```js
const s = "  one  two   three ";
const parts = s.trim().split(/\s+/);
console.log(parts.length, parts[1]);
```

shift() bo‘sh massivda qanday? ```js
const a = [];
console.log(a.shift(), a.length);
```

Object.freeze ta’siri: ```js
const o = Object.freeze({x:1, y:{z:2}});
o.x = 9;
o.y.z = 9;
console.log(o.x, o.y.z);
```

splice bilan bo‘sh o‘chirish: ```js
const a = [1,2,3];
console.log(a.length);
```

push va pop bilan stek misoli: Yakuniy massiv? ```js
const s = [];
s.push(1); s.push(2); s.pop(); s.push(3);
console.log(s);
```

Object.entries bilan hisoblash: ```js
const prices = {apple:2, banana:1, cherry:3};
const total = Object.entries(prices)
  .reduce((sum, [k,v]) => sum + v, 0);
console.log(total);
```

split('') va reverse().join('') bilan satrni ag‘darish: ```js
const s = "aba";
const r = s.split('').reverse().join('');
console.log(s === r);
```

splice qaytargan massiv uzunligi: ```js
const a = [0,1,2,3,4];
const r = a.splice(1,3);
console.log(r.length, a);
```

Object kalitiga nuqta va qavs bilan murojaat: to‘g‘ri natija? ```js
const key = 'first-name';
const user = {'first-name': 'Ali', firstName: 'Vali'};
console.log(user[key], user.firstName);
```
